title: The Incredible Shrinking Supreme Court Docket
itunes:title: The Incredible Shrinking Supreme Court Docket
description:
Constitutional law expert Stephen Vladeck, a professor at the University of Texas Law School, discusses why the Supreme Court is handing down its fewest decisions in decades this term.

June Grasso hosts.
